title: Ep. 466 - The Gaslighting Left
description:
Boris Johnson wins big for Brexit just hours after the media say he’s down, Pelosi says the case for impeachment remains very strong after dropping the only impeachment offense charge she had on President Trump, and James Comey insists the IG vindicated him just days after the IG explicitly did not vindicate him.
